{"tid":2040750,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PS4 中國版封鎖外服   只玩經審批遊戲","createTime":"2020-05-28T19:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T05:33:58.000Z","uid":85180,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"89a5abf1dcaec129a4972aa50cc154b646d894ec","tid":2040750,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T19:55:47.000Z","msg":"PS4 中國版封鎖外服   只玩經審批遊戲<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/sony_ps41tb_sony_playstation_4_pro_1473361530000_1280641-900x900.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2Fsony_ps41tb_sony_playstation_4_pro_1473361530000_1280641-900x900.jpg&h=1407c192&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上周報道過 Xbox One 進行更新後，中國網民無法利用破解方式瀏覽其他地區的商店，以及遊玩國外遊戲；昨日（27 日），有中國網民發現同樣的情況竟然蔓延至中國版 PlayStation 4。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/TIM%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%8720200527204738.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2FTIM%25E5%259B%25BE%25E7%2589%258720200527204738.png&h=f3bc3ddf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為要提升性能，PS4 中國版推出了 7.51 版本更新。但是有玩家發現更新後，不能進行新註冊和登入其他地區包括香港的伺服器帳號，同時出現「此帳戶無法使用這台 PS4」提示訊息。這代表中國玩家今後無辦法再登入其他地區的伺服器，以購買和遊玩遊戲，只能購買中國版通過中國官方審查的遊戲。解決方法只有通過硬碟備份功能降級到上一個版本，又或者不升級最新版本。<br />\n<br />\nPlayStation 中國商店在本月初已經發生暫停服務的事件，指出由於「系統升級」，因而暫停服務，但卻沒有公布恢復時間，變相「無限期」暫停服務。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n資料來源：台灣NowNews"},{"pid":"9f4a9c77019a8e81e6e8a50bac43882029cb989b","tid":2040750,"uid":344072,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T19:58:42.000Z","msg":"不升級最新版本...<br />\n結果咪又係冇得連線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1bd62a6f487e1b360829fa25c98dcfcc4308e11","tid":2040750,"uid":176282,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2